	<li><a href="https://onlinebooks.library.upenn.edu/"><strong>Online Books Page from the University of Pennsylvania Library</strong></a> - A librarian-curated archive of more than a million works free for personal, noncommercial use.</li>
	<li><a href="https://openlibrary.org/"><strong>OpenLibrary</strong></a> - a project to create a comprehensive, open library for the world, with many ebooks available for checkout.</li>
	<li><a href="https://www.gutenberg.org"><strong>Project Gutenberg</strong></a> - Birthplace of the free eBook, Project Gutenberg offers over 39,000 free eBooks in all formats.</li>
